Invocation Name: driving sounds
des: Vroom vroom, let the sounds of the road whisk you to sleep. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Driving Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
